c: 40
v: 74
t: "Apart from God? (Where are now those whose help you expected?)?\" They will say: \"They have failed us – or rather, we were not invoking before any (real) thing (which had part in Divinity or Lordship or absolute Sovereignty).\" Thus does God lead astray the unbelievers (those who willfully disregard the truth and refuse to believe in it)"